title: Final Fantasy XIII PS3 Theme
description:
Final Fantasy XIII PS3 Theme

 - 5x 1920 x 1080 background images
 - Custom Icons


Neither the images or the icons are my own work. I have simply done some mega basic editing of the images and slapped them together with some icons from another theme. But as an FFXIII fan I think this is an awesome PS3 theme.
